precis:
Re-appointment of certain persons as full-time temporary members of the
Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee
Board (Montreal Regional Office) to hold office during good behaviour for
a term of two years, effective September 1, 1992.
(Dorothy A. Wills, Anjou, Quebec; Pierre Bernier, Charlesbourg, Quebec;
Marilyn Hébert, Ste-Sophie, Quebec; and Georges Gustave,
Rivière-des-Prairies, Quebec)
